1.  in a terminal, move to the folder where you want to install davitpy
2.  type 'git clone https://github.com/vtsuperdarn/davitpy.git'
3.  add the following liens to your ~/.bashrc

		export DAVITPY="/davitpy"
		export PATH=${DAVITPY}"/bin":${PATH}

4.	open a new terminal, type 'davitpy', and enjoy